##Layer 2: Weekend`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`To create the weekend schedule, click `}<strong parentName="li">{`Add Another Layer`}</strong>{` below the previous one. The second layer will be the `}<em parentName="li">{`weekend`}</em>{` layer.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ol">{`Add the layer members and set the rotation type as `}<strong parentName="li">{`daily`}</strong>{` with a handoff time of `}<strong parentName="li">{`00:00`}</strong>{` so users start at midnight.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ol">{`Since this layer is only on Saturday and Sunday, you will need to click the check box to `}<strong parentName="li">{`Restrict on-call shifts to specific times`}</strong>{`. Restrict on-call shift to `}<em parentName="li">{`times-of-the-week`}</em>{` from Saturday 00:00 â€“ Monday 00:00 to create the weekend rotation.
